nodes.text: The Bryx Sector Force was a Rebel Alliance Sector Force, assigned to the Bryx sector during the Galactic Civil War. Like most of the other Sector Force, it was created from a local resistance movement: the Bryx Freedom Fighters, a Separatist holdouts force active in the sector following the end of the Clone Wars. It was led by former Separatist General Horn Ambigene.
